dct_description_sm: At head of title: The Century atlas. Relief shown by hachures, and spot heights. Depth shown by isolines and soundings. In upper right margin: No. 112. Prime meridian: Greenwich. Inset: Madagascar and Comoro Islands (French). Same scale as main map. 1 map: col., mounted on cloth; 27 x 39 cm
